Name: MODE OF TRANSPORT
Explanation: A GENERAL MODE OF TRANSPORTATION USED IN THE SURFACE MOVEMENT OF PERSONNEL AND/OR CARGO.

Name: CONVEYANCE
Explanation: IDENTIFICATION OF THE PARTICULAR TRANSPORTATION MEANS EMPLOYED, E.G., FIRST TRAIN, 2ND SERIAL, OR BARGE.

Name: SURFACE TRANSPORT MEANS
Explanation: THE SPECIFIC TYPE CONVEYANCE EMPLOYED WITHIN THE SURFACE TRANSPORTATION MODE OF CONCERN.
